headline: FactSet price target lowered to $448 from $470 at Evercore ISI
summary: Evercore ISI lowered the firm’s price target on FactSet (FDS) to $448 from $470 and keeps an In Line rating on the shares. FactSet’s upcoming fiscal Q3 results may reveal challenges as estimates have been lowered due to macro volatility and leadership changes, says the analyst, whose anticipated EPS of $4.26 falls short of consensus.
